      "comment": "COLOSSAL HOPE (4) is a progressive gelding who took his record to five from six when he led and fought well to win in his first visit to this circuit last time. That saw him unbeaten at the mile and he looks a big chance to deliver again. DUTY OF CARE (3) has been racing well and has the hoof on the till after placing in his last four outings at this circuit and distance. Has come from wider barriers at his last couple. Go well again. Former Kiwi OHOKA COBRA NZ (7) showed improvement in his second local appearance and could progress further. GIPSY PRINCESS (10) draws deep but recorded three successive seconds here earlier in the campaign, one from this barrier when she missed by just a nose.",
